title: macbook 12” early 2015
message: Hello i have a macbook 12” early 2015 that is not charging at all, I've tried a new charging port and also a charging port Flex with a new battery and it is still pulling 0 amps. Board  [SIZE=3][FONT=arial]820-00045-10   [/FONT][/SIZE]any recommendations on where to start

title: macbook 12” early 2015
message:
Not charging, or not starting at all???

Be aware, all these boards end with dead CPU...

title: macbook 12” early 2015
message:
Then let the baterry out.
You don't need it, until get the board starting on charger alone.

Post diode mode (red probe at ground) at 3V3_AON power rail.
Also check at PPBUS_G3H and 3V3_G3H.

USB-C meter is stuck at 5V?

title: macbook 12” early 2015
message: yes USB-C meter is stuck at 5V
